## Ước lượng effort

| Phase | Effort | LLM Cost | Blocking? |
|---|---|---|---|
| Phase 0: Exploration | 1h | $0 | No |
| Phase 1: Documents + Text Units | 2h | $0 | No |
| Phase 2: Entities | 1h | $0 | No |
| Phase 3: Relationships | 2h | $0 | No |
| Phase 4: Communities (Leiden) | 2h | $0 | No |
| Phase 5: Community Reports | 3h | $0-5 | **Yes — needs LLM** |
| Phase 6: Embeddings + LanceDB | 2h | $0 | **Yes — needs Ollama running** |
| Phase 7: Assembly + Query Test | 1h | $0 | No |
| Phase 8: Backend Integration | 4h | $0 | No |
| **Total** | **~18h** | **$0-5** | |

## Rủi ro & Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|
| `other_doc_id` cast fails (non-numeric values) | Mất edges | Phase 0 check, filter invalid, log count |
| Orphan doc_ids (in rels but not in meta) | Broken graph | Inner join only, report coverage |
| Community count quá lớn (>1000) | LLM cost tăng | Chỉ generate reports cho level 0-1 |
| Embedding dim mismatch | LanceDB error | Verify dim trước, update settings |
| Qwen free tier rate limit | Slow community reports | Checkpoint + resume, patience |
| Content HTML complex (tables, images) | Bad text quality | Robust `bs4` stripping, fallback to title-only |

